WEBVTT

00:01.167 --> 00:02.711
[melodic whistling]

00:02.794 --> 00:04.254
[smacking]

00:04.337 --> 00:05.380
[exhaling deeply]

00:05.463 --> 00:07.757
thump.
both: WHOA.

00:07.841 --> 00:09.634
- ♪ HERE WE GO 'CAUSE WE'RE
FANBOY AND CHUM CHUM ♪

00:09.718 --> 00:11.094
♪ A LITTLE CUCKOO,
FANBOY AND CHUM CHUM ♪

00:11.177 --> 00:12.595
♪ WE'RE AMAZING,
TOTALLY CRAZY ♪

00:12.679 --> 00:13.596
♪ FANBOY AND CHUM CHUM ♪

00:13.680 --> 00:15.098
♪ COME ON, EVERYBODY, SING ♪

00:15.181 --> 00:16.808
♪ WE'RE GONNA SCREAM
AT THE TOP OF OUR LUNGS ♪

00:16.891 --> 00:18.435
♪ WE'RE GONNA FLY
AND HAVE SOME FUN ♪

00:18.518 --> 00:20.478
♪ WE DON'T CARE IF YOU STARE ♪

00:20.562 --> 00:21.479
♪ OR EVEN
LOOK AT OUR UNDERWEAR ♪

00:21.563 --> 00:23.898
both: ♪ BRAIN ♪

00:23.982 --> 00:25.942
♪ FREEZE ♪

00:26.025 --> 00:27.152
♪ OOH ♪

00:27.235 --> 00:28.528
♪ BRAIN FREEZE. ♪

00:28.611 --> 00:30.321
- ♪ BUH-BUH, BAH,
BAH, BAH, BAH, BAH, BAH ♪

00:30.405 --> 00:32.281
♪ BUH-BUH, BAH, BAH-BAH,
BUH, BAH-BAH, BAH ♪

00:32.365 --> 00:33.199
♪ BAH, BAH, BAH, BAH ♪

00:33.283 --> 00:35.827
♪ BUH-BUH, BAH-BAH,
BUH-BAH, BAH ♪

00:35.910 --> 00:37.746
♪ COME AND SCREAM
AT THE TOP OF YOUR LUNGS ♪

00:37.829 --> 00:39.122
♪ COME AND FLY
AND HAVE SOME FUN ♪

00:39.205 --> 00:40.123
♪ BUH-BUH, BAH ♪

00:40.206 --> 00:41.624
♪ BUH-BUH, BAH ♪

00:41.708 --> 00:43.126
♪ BUH-BUH, BAH, BAH,
FANBOY AND CHUM CHUM ♪

00:43.209 --> 00:44.335
both: OH.
- THAT'S NICE.

00:46.296 --> 00:48.256
[coughing and sneezing]

01:00.977 --> 01:01.561
[thunder crashes]

01:01.644 --> 01:04.480
[rain pounding]

01:04.563 --> 01:06.775
[all groan]

01:06.858 --> 01:08.401
both: RAIN!

01:08.485 --> 01:09.778
♪ RAIN, RAIN, COME AGAIN ♪

01:09.861 --> 01:12.030
♪ GIVE US WATER ON THE BRAIN ♪

01:12.113 --> 01:14.866
- ♪ SPLASH, SPLASH,
SPLASH, SPLASH, SPLASH! ♪

01:14.949 --> 01:16.618
- ♪ SPLASH, SPLASH, SPLASH,
SPLASH, SPLASH, SPLASH! ♪

01:16.701 --> 01:18.578
[both sniffing]

01:18.661 --> 01:22.999
[sneezing]

01:23.082 --> 01:25.084
[hacking and sneezing]

01:27.670 --> 01:28.838
- UGH.

01:28.922 --> 01:32.717
- I'M GONNA WRITE THAT NO-GOOD
MOTHER NATURE SUCH A LETTER.

01:32.801 --> 01:34.594
- LOOK AT THE BRIGHT SIDE.

01:34.677 --> 01:36.304
[snorting]

01:36.387 --> 01:37.639
WE MAY HAVE COLDS,

01:37.722 --> 01:39.474
BUT AT LEAST WE GET TO SPEND
THE DAY AT HOME TOGETHER,

01:39.557 --> 01:41.518
BEST PAL O' MINE.

01:41.601 --> 01:43.436
- THAT'S TRUE, BUDDY.

01:43.520 --> 01:45.647
WELL, WE BETTER CALL IN SICK.

01:45.730 --> 01:49.025
[phone ringing]

01:49.108 --> 01:50.235
- FROSTY MART.

01:50.318 --> 01:54.739
HOW MAY I MAKE YOUR DAY
MORE FROSTENTATIOUS?

01:54.823 --> 01:55.698
- HEY, LENNY.

01:55.782 --> 01:57.408
CHUM CHUM AND I HAVE COLDS,

01:57.492 --> 01:58.868
SO WE'RE NOT GONNA BE ABLE
TO MAKE IT IN

01:58.952 --> 02:01.204
FOR TODAY'S USUAL MADCAP HIJINKS
AND TOMFOOLERY.

02:01.287 --> 02:02.747
REALLY SORRY.

02:02.831 --> 02:05.208
- UGH, NO PROBLEM.

02:05.291 --> 02:06.543
STAY AWAY AS LONG AS YOU LIKE.

02:06.626 --> 02:07.627
LONGER, EVEN.

02:07.710 --> 02:08.919
- THANKS, LENNY.

02:09.002 --> 02:11.381
WE'LL TRY AND PULL A DOUBLE
NEXT WEEK.

02:11.464 --> 02:11.923
OOH, NACHOS.

02:12.006 --> 02:13.049
- HEY, THOSE ARE--

02:13.132 --> 02:18.221
- NOW WE'RE NO WORK
AND ALL PLAY.

02:18.304 --> 02:20.849
- SO WHAT SHOULD WE DO?

02:20.932 --> 02:23.560
- I THINK TODAY IS THE DAY
WE FINALLY REACH THE BOTTOM

02:23.643 --> 02:25.687
OF THAT BOX.

02:30.817 --> 02:34.821
- FANBOY TIME SAYS
TEN SECONDS LATER.

02:34.904 --> 02:37.282
- BOY, THAT BOTTOM REALLY
SNEAKS UP ON YOU.

02:37.365 --> 02:38.992
- I'LL SAY.

02:39.075 --> 02:40.201
TV?

02:40.285 --> 02:41.870
- NOTHING ELSE TO DO.

02:41.953 --> 02:43.371
[remote clicking]

02:43.454 --> 02:48.501
- UGH.

02:50.670 --> 02:52.922
OH, MAN.

02:53.006 --> 02:55.133
THE BATTERIES ARE DEAD.

02:55.216 --> 02:59.387
ONE OF US IS GONNA HAVE
TO GET UP AND TURN ON THE TV.

02:59.470 --> 03:01.097
[coughs weakly]

03:01.180 --> 03:02.015
- IN MY CONDITION?

03:02.098 --> 03:03.850
UH-UH, TOO RISKY.

03:03.933 --> 03:06.269
- I'LL DO IT.

03:06.352 --> 03:08.354
GAHH!

03:08.438 --> 03:11.274
SO WEAK.

03:11.357 --> 03:15.612
FANBOY, TURN ON THE TV FOR ME.

03:15.695 --> 03:16.321
[gasping]

03:16.404 --> 03:19.407
- OH, CHUM CHUM, IS THAT YOU?

03:19.490 --> 03:22.577
I BELIEVE I'M SUFFERING
FROM FEVER BLINDNESS.

03:22.660 --> 03:27.040
- SO YOU'RE REALLY NOT GONNA DO
THIS ONE LITTLE FAVOR FOR ME?

03:27.123 --> 03:29.334
- I BELIEVE MY RECORD'S CLEAR
ON THE MATTER.

03:29.417 --> 03:30.543
- FINE.

03:30.627 --> 03:32.337
I DIDN'T WANT TO WATCH
TV ANYWAY.

03:32.420 --> 03:33.379
- ME NEITHER.

03:33.463 --> 03:34.297
- GREAT!

03:34.380 --> 03:35.381
- TERRIFIC!

03:35.465 --> 03:36.591
ACHOO!

03:36.674 --> 03:39.135
[clears throat]

03:39.218 --> 03:40.637
- DO YOU MIND?

03:40.720 --> 03:42.430
I HAVE TO BREATHE THIS AIR TOO.

03:42.513 --> 03:44.849
- OH, MY APOLOGIES.

03:44.933 --> 03:46.851
- ACHOO!

03:46.935 --> 03:50.939
- UGH, EVER HEAR OF A TISSUE,
FRIEND?

03:51.022 --> 03:53.149
- PARDON ME, BUDDY.

03:53.232 --> 03:54.400
[snorting]

03:54.484 --> 03:56.319
- ACHOO!

03:56.402 --> 03:57.737
- YOU DID THAT ON PURPOSE.

03:57.820 --> 03:58.988
- NUH-UH.

03:59.072 --> 04:02.784
IF I'D HAVE DONE IT ON PURPOSE,
I WOULD HAVE DONE THIS.

04:02.867 --> 04:07.497
[in slo-mo]
ACHOO!

04:07.580 --> 04:10.750
[splattering]

04:10.833 --> 04:15.254
- [groans]

04:15.338 --> 04:16.630
THIS ENDS NOW!

04:16.714 --> 04:18.716
- YOU ARE!

04:18.800 --> 04:20.218
[both growling]

04:22.762 --> 04:26.516
[both screaming]

04:26.599 --> 04:28.643
[doorbell rings]

04:28.726 --> 04:29.727
YOU EXPECTING SOMEONE?

04:29.811 --> 04:31.396
- NOT ME.

04:33.773 --> 04:35.149
both: KYLE?

04:35.233 --> 04:37.110
[thunder crashes]

04:37.193 --> 04:38.778
- WHAT ARE YOU DOING HERE?

04:38.861 --> 04:40.989
- OBVIOUSLY, I WOULDN'T BE HERE
UNLESS THIS WAS AN EMERGENCY.

04:41.072 --> 04:42.782
I GOT CAUGHT OUTSIDE
IN THE RAIN,

04:42.865 --> 04:44.826
WHICH AS YOU KNOW

04:44.909 --> 04:46.953
IS LIKE ACID
TO WIZARDS.

04:47.036 --> 04:48.663
ALSO, THIS SEEMS TO BE
ACID RAIN.

04:48.746 --> 04:51.541
SO COULD I--

04:51.624 --> 04:53.501
- STAY HERE
AND PLAY WITH ME ALL DAY?

04:53.584 --> 04:56.254
OF COURSE, OLD FRIEND.

04:56.337 --> 04:58.840
- KYLE, WOULDN'T YOU RATHER
PLAY WITH ME?

04:58.923 --> 05:01.509
- ARE YOU KIDDING?

05:01.592 --> 05:04.887
HE IS CLEARLY HERE
TO PLAY WITH ME.

05:04.971 --> 05:07.098
- [groaning]

05:07.181 --> 05:08.057
smack!

05:08.141 --> 05:09.142
[growls]

05:10.476 --> 05:13.563
I'M NOT HERE TO PLAY
WITH EITHER OF YOU.

05:13.646 --> 05:14.731
REMEMBER THE RAIN?

05:14.814 --> 05:16.107
HELLO?

05:16.190 --> 05:17.608
WHY WOULD I WANT TO SPEND
ANY TIME AT ALL

05:17.692 --> 05:19.318
WITH YOU SNOT-FILLED
TROLL BABIES?

05:19.402 --> 05:20.611
both: 'CAUSE YOU'RE
MY BEST FRIEND.

05:20.695 --> 05:21.654
[gasping]

05:21.738 --> 05:24.323
[growling]

05:24.407 --> 05:26.242
- YOUR BEST FRIEND?

05:26.325 --> 05:27.118
REALLY?

05:27.201 --> 05:28.244
I DON'T KNOW WHAT TO SAY.

05:28.327 --> 05:30.288
I-I ALWAYS ASSUMED
YOU DESPISED ME

05:30.371 --> 05:32.790
AS MUCH AS I DESPISE YOU.

05:32.874 --> 05:33.875
- PISH TO THE POSH, KYLE.

05:33.958 --> 05:37.378
YOU'RE LIKE, UM, THE BEST GUY
TO HANG OUT WITH.

05:37.462 --> 05:39.047
SO MUCH COOLER THAN...

05:39.130 --> 05:41.799
- FANBOY, WHO NEVER
PAYS ATTENTION TO PEOPLE.

05:41.883 --> 05:44.802
ALL FANBOY DOES IS TALK
AND TALK AND--

05:44.886 --> 05:48.806
OH!

05:48.890 --> 05:50.600
- SO, BEST FRIEND KYLE,

05:50.683 --> 05:51.100
WANT TO PLAY A GAME?

05:51.184 --> 05:51.768
- MINE!
- NO.

05:51.851 --> 05:54.270
- NO, MINE!

05:54.353 --> 05:56.064
- YOU'RE MAKING THIS MORE
DIFFICULT THAN IT HAS TO BE.

05:56.147 --> 05:57.774
- JUST TO BE CLEAR,

05:57.857 --> 05:59.108
YOU'RE FIGHTING OVER ME?

05:59.192 --> 06:02.653
WELL, I DON'T KNOW WHAT TO SAY.

06:02.737 --> 06:05.448
I'VE NEVER ACTUALLY HAD ANYONE
WANT TO PAY WITH ME BEFORE.

06:05.531 --> 06:07.116
both: I DO!

06:07.200 --> 06:12.622
- ALL THOSE GAMES OF SOLITAIRE,
HIDING AND NO ONE SEEKING.

06:12.705 --> 06:13.623
RIGHT THEN.

06:13.706 --> 06:15.375
THIS IS A MOMENTOUS DECISION.

06:15.458 --> 06:17.627
WHO SHALL GAIN THE PRIVILEGE
OF BEING MY BEST FRIEND

06:17.710 --> 06:18.669
AND PLAYING WITH ME?

06:18.753 --> 06:20.004
HMM?

06:20.088 --> 06:21.297
- [gasping and moaning]

06:21.380 --> 06:22.757
- [sniveling]

06:22.840 --> 06:24.801
- ARE THESE THE ONLY CHOICES?

06:24.884 --> 06:29.472
- BEFORE YOU CHOOSE, KYLE,
JUST CONSIDER THIS.

06:29.555 --> 06:32.767
- [screaming]

06:32.850 --> 06:33.893
slam!

06:33.976 --> 06:38.314
- WELL, THAT DOES
SIMPLIFY THINGS.

06:38.397 --> 06:39.315
- [humming cheerfully]

06:39.398 --> 06:40.650
- SO WHAT DO YOU
WANT TO DO FIRST?

06:40.733 --> 06:42.110
YOU WANT TO PLAY DEAD ARM,
CHARLIE HORSE,

06:42.193 --> 06:43.820
EYESIES POKESIES?

06:43.903 --> 06:46.989
- PERHAPS A BOARD GAME WOULD BE
MORE TO MY TASTE.

06:47.073 --> 06:49.450
- OKAY, CHECK THIS OUT.

06:49.534 --> 06:50.409
[crashing]

06:50.493 --> 06:53.496
[cat yowling]

06:53.579 --> 06:55.164
LET'S SEE WHAT WE GOT.

06:55.248 --> 06:56.666
KILLER ROBOT FRENZY,
ZOMBIE ATTACK,

06:56.749 --> 06:58.501
VIOLENCE FIGHT,
VIOLENCE FIGHT 2.

06:58.584 --> 06:59.627
NOW WITH MORE VIOLENCE.

06:59.710 --> 07:01.087
- OOH!

07:01.170 --> 07:03.548
MR. UNICORN'S TEDDY BEAR
DRESS UP FASHION SHOW.

07:03.631 --> 07:07.718
- EH, CHUM CHUM AND I SORT OF
MELTED ALL THOSE PIECES

07:07.802 --> 07:08.761
TO PUT THEM
OUT OF THEIR LAMENESS.

07:08.845 --> 07:10.972
- PITY.

07:11.055 --> 07:13.432
OKAY THEN,
HOW ABOUT CHINESE CHECKERS?

07:13.516 --> 07:14.642
HMM.

07:14.725 --> 07:18.062
THEN AGAIN, THAT MAY GET
A BIT HIGH-SPIRITED,

07:18.146 --> 07:20.189
WHAT WITH THE SPICE
OF THE ORIENT.

07:20.273 --> 07:23.776
PERHAPS JUST DOMESTIC CHECKERS.

07:23.860 --> 07:25.570
- I CHOOSE--

07:25.653 --> 07:27.071
- I CHOOSE BLACK.

07:27.155 --> 07:30.533
- OH, WELL, CHUM CHUM USUALLY
LETS ME CHOOSE BLACK,

07:30.616 --> 07:33.536
YOU KNOW, FOR NINJAS.

07:33.619 --> 07:34.787
HIYA, HA!

07:34.871 --> 07:37.039
- WELL,
I'M YOUR BEST FRIEND NOW.

07:37.123 --> 07:39.834
AND I CHOOSE TO CHOOSE FIRST.

07:39.917 --> 07:41.043
- UH, SURE.

07:41.127 --> 07:44.922
OKAY, I GUESS.

07:45.006 --> 07:46.174
- I JUMPED YOU.

07:46.257 --> 07:47.216
DEAL WITH THAT.

07:47.300 --> 07:48.134
- HIYA!

07:48.217 --> 07:49.969
- WHAT ON EARTH ARE YOU DOING?

07:50.052 --> 07:52.054
- PLAYING!

07:52.138 --> 07:53.055
YOU GOT TO MAKE
THE EVIL ENERGY DISKS

07:53.139 --> 07:56.017
JUMP INTO THE BLACK HOLE.

07:56.100 --> 08:00.646
- WHY DO YOU INSIST ON
BESMIRCHING SUCH A NOBLE GAME?

08:00.730 --> 08:01.564
- WHAT?

08:01.647 --> 08:04.442
HOW DO YOU PLAY DEATH CHECKERS?

08:04.525 --> 08:07.069
- OBVIOUSLY, I'VE CHOSEN
THE WRONG BEST FRIEND.

08:07.153 --> 08:08.070
- BUT KYLE--

08:08.154 --> 08:09.071
[screaming]

08:09.155 --> 08:10.156
- COME ON, BEST FRIEND KYLE.

08:10.239 --> 08:14.994
HE DOESN'T DESERVE YOU.

08:15.077 --> 08:16.245
- EEP!

08:16.329 --> 08:17.914
OW.

08:17.997 --> 08:22.543
- SO EXACTLY HOW DOES ONE
PLAY ACTION FIGURINES?

08:22.627 --> 08:23.753
- IT'S EASY.

08:23.836 --> 08:25.922
YOU JUST MOVE AROUND
AND MAKE THEM FIGHT.

08:26.005 --> 08:28.591
- OH, HOW DELIGHTFULLY LOWBROW.

08:28.674 --> 08:30.092
EN GARDE.

08:30.176 --> 08:30.927
STAND AND DELIVER.

08:31.010 --> 08:33.846
[both giggling]

08:33.929 --> 08:36.474
THERE, I HAVE GIVEN YOU
WHAT-FOR.

08:36.557 --> 08:38.558
- NOPE, I MOVED.

08:38.643 --> 08:39.602
- YOU DIDN'T MOVE.

08:39.684 --> 08:40.645
- I'M TOO QUICK.

08:40.727 --> 08:41.645
YOU DIDN'T SEE.

08:41.729 --> 08:42.855
BUT NOW I CHOP YOUR ARM OFF.

08:42.938 --> 08:44.774
- HUH?

08:44.857 --> 08:45.942
OH.

08:46.025 --> 08:47.276
ALL RIGHT THEN.

08:47.360 --> 08:51.364
PERHAPS YOU'LL FEEL THE FORCE
OF BOTH MY PARRY AND MY THRUST.

08:51.447 --> 08:53.699
[giggling]

08:53.783 --> 08:55.034
OH, HO!

08:55.117 --> 08:56.160
I'VE CUT YOU TO THE QUICK.

08:56.244 --> 08:57.161
- UH-UH.

08:57.245 --> 08:59.330
YOU BOUNCED OFF MY FORCE FIELD.

08:59.413 --> 09:01.082
- FORCE FIELD?

09:01.165 --> 09:02.625
NINJA'S DON'T HAVE FORCE F--

09:02.708 --> 09:05.836
- AND THEN I USE MY SONIC RAY
TO PRETZEL-IZE YOUR LEGS.

09:05.920 --> 09:07.004
- DON'T DO THAT.

09:07.088 --> 09:08.214
- OH.

09:08.297 --> 09:10.508
- OOO, SONIC TURBO NINJAS.

09:10.591 --> 09:13.594
DID YOU USE YOUR MYSTICAL
THROWING COW?

09:13.678 --> 09:14.512
HERE.

09:14.595 --> 09:16.222
- OOO, GOOD CALL.

09:18.516 --> 09:19.600
- SO WE'RE GOING TO PLAY

09:19.684 --> 09:22.270
LOOSEY-GOOSEY WITH THE RULES,
ARE WE?

09:22.353 --> 09:24.438
WELL, WHAT DO YOU THINK OF THIS?

09:26.148 --> 09:29.026
[grunting]

09:31.404 --> 09:32.321
[sighs]

09:32.405 --> 09:33.155
THERE.

09:33.239 --> 09:36.659
TASTE OF YOUR OWN MEDICINE.

09:36.742 --> 09:37.660
[groans]

09:37.743 --> 09:38.661
- MISSED ME.

09:38.744 --> 09:39.578
- HUH?

09:39.662 --> 09:40.621
- AND YOUR HEAD EXPLODES.

09:40.705 --> 09:41.706
[explosion]

09:41.789 --> 09:42.748
- GRR!

09:42.832 --> 09:45.501
YOU'RE CHEATERS,
CHARLATANS

09:45.584 --> 09:49.171
WITH YOUR MADE-UP RULES
AND YOUR AIRBORNE LIVESTOCK!

09:49.255 --> 09:52.258
I CALL SHENANIGANS!

09:52.341 --> 09:53.217
both: [gasp]

09:53.301 --> 09:54.343
EEE!

09:54.427 --> 09:55.386
SHENANIGANS!

09:55.469 --> 09:57.221
[alarm blaring]

09:57.305 --> 10:00.850
[kids cheering]

10:00.933 --> 10:02.518
- HUH?

10:02.601 --> 10:07.648
- GENTLEMEN,
SHENANIGANS HAS BEEN CALLED.

10:07.732 --> 10:08.858
- WHAT'S HAPPENING?

10:08.941 --> 10:11.110
- SHENANIGANS IS THE BEST
GAME WE'VE GOT.

10:11.193 --> 10:14.113
WAY TO GO, KYLE.

10:14.196 --> 10:14.697
- HUH?

10:14.780 --> 10:19.702
- SEND IN THE CLONES!

10:19.785 --> 10:21.454
all: SHENANIGANS! SHENANIGANS!

10:21.537 --> 10:23.372
SHENANIGANS! SHENANIGANS!
SHENANIGANS!

10:23.456 --> 10:26.459
- [screaming]

10:30.129 --> 10:32.048
NO, NO, NO!

10:32.131 --> 10:34.675
both: PANCAKE FIGHT!

10:34.759 --> 10:36.135
- OH, HELP!

10:36.218 --> 10:38.679
- OOH, A RED-HOT HUCKLEBERRY,
AND ON YOUR FIRST TRY.

10:38.763 --> 10:42.099
- THAT GETS YOU
A SKY-HIGH ROUGH RIDE.

10:42.183 --> 10:45.895
- [screaming]

10:51.650 --> 10:55.237
[muffled speech]

10:55.321 --> 10:57.656
AND I REFUSE TO SPEND
ONE MORE MOMENT

10:57.740 --> 10:59.533
IN THIS NUTHOUSE!

10:59.617 --> 11:02.620
LET ME OUT OF HERE!

11:02.703 --> 11:03.662
- OKIE DOKIE.

11:03.746 --> 11:04.663
KYLE CALLS OUTSIES.

11:04.747 --> 11:06.165
[alarm blaring]

11:06.248 --> 11:06.999
[rain pounding]

11:07.083 --> 11:09.251
- [screaming]

11:09.335 --> 11:10.878
OW.

11:10.961 --> 11:12.254
- GOOD GAME. GOOD GAME.
GOOD GAME.

11:12.338 --> 11:13.756
GOOD GAME. GOOD GAME.

11:13.839 --> 11:15.257
- HOW FUN WAS THAT?

11:15.341 --> 11:17.134
- SUPER FUN!

11:17.218 --> 11:20.096
HEY, I'M NOT SICK

11:20.179 --> 11:21.222
OR SICK OF YOU ANYMORE.

11:21.305 --> 11:23.432
- ME NEITHER.

11:23.516 --> 11:26.310
SUCH IS THE ENDURING GIFT
OF SHENANIGANS.

11:26.394 --> 11:27.436
- HMM.

11:27.520 --> 11:30.773
- CHUM CHUM,
LET'S PROMISE TO NEVER DO

11:30.856 --> 11:32.233
WHATEVER GOT US MAD
AT EACH OTHER

11:32.316 --> 11:34.568
IN THE FIRST PLACE EVER AGAIN,
WHATEVER THAT WAS.

11:34.652 --> 11:37.571
- IT'S A DEAL, BEST FRIEND.

11:37.655 --> 11:39.407
WANT TO GO PLAY OUT IN THE RAIN?

11:39.490 --> 11:41.117
- YOU READ MY MIND, BEST FRIEND.

11:41.200 --> 11:44.954
YOU READ MY MIND.

11:46.122 --> 11:49.208
[goofy music]

11:49.291 --> 11:55.131
♪ ♪

11:55.214 --> 11:58.175
[all cheering]

12:02.346 --> 12:03.597
- HEY, HEY.

12:03.681 --> 12:05.141
PERHAPS YOU DIDN'T SEE
OUR STORE POLICY.

12:05.224 --> 12:10.604
"BUY OR BE BOPPED!"

12:10.688 --> 12:12.982
PLEASURE DOING BUSINESS.

12:13.065 --> 12:14.316
[laughter]

12:14.400 --> 12:15.818
- BOOG, WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

12:15.901 --> 12:17.987
YOU CAN'T SELL JUNK
IN THE PARKING LOT.

12:18.070 --> 12:21.115
- I'M JUST GETTING RID
OF JUNK I DON'T NEED.

12:21.198 --> 12:22.533
-<i> CAT MASSAGE MADE EASY?</i>

12:22.616 --> 12:24.034
STRESS TO ITCH CREAM?

12:24.118 --> 12:25.161
HEY, THIS STUFF IS MINE!

12:25.244 --> 12:26.203
- LIKE I SAID.

12:26.287 --> 12:27.955
I DON'T NEED IT.

12:28.038 --> 12:32.209
[laughs]

12:32.293 --> 12:34.086
- PARDON ME, MY GOOD MAN.

12:34.170 --> 12:36.255
WOULD YOU MIND TAKING US THROUGH
THIS FINE SELECTION

12:36.338 --> 12:37.214
OF BROKEN ALARM CLOCKS?

12:37.298 --> 12:39.175
- MY PLEASURE.

12:39.258 --> 12:40.134
THIS FIRST ONE--

12:40.217 --> 12:41.177
- [gasps]

12:41.260 --> 12:43.179
WHAT IS THAT?

12:43.262 --> 12:44.096
- OH, THAT?

12:44.180 --> 12:46.682
IT'S THE CHILDHOOD BUBBLE
I GREW UP IN,

12:46.765 --> 12:52.438
ON ACCOUNT OF I WAS ALLERGIC TO,
LIKE, EVERYTHING.

12:52.521 --> 12:56.525
- BOOG, HONEY, HAVE YOU FINISHED
YOUR GLASS OF AIR?

12:56.609 --> 12:58.235
- I'M DOING IT NOW, MA!

12:58.319 --> 13:02.031
GEEZ, GET OFF MY BACK ALREADY.

13:02.114 --> 13:03.365
[gasps]

13:03.449 --> 13:07.828
[popping]

13:07.912 --> 13:09.955
STUPID AIR ALLERGY.

13:10.039 --> 13:11.123
I HATE THIS BUBBLE!

13:11.207 --> 13:13.626
OW!

13:13.709 --> 13:15.711
IT BOP-FIRED ON ME.

13:15.794 --> 13:18.547
SOMEDAY I'M GONNA GET OUT
OF THIS BUBBLE

13:18.631 --> 13:21.300
AND INFLICT THAT KIND OF PAIN
ON OTHERS.

13:21.383 --> 13:23.093
SOMEDAY.

13:23.177 --> 13:25.429
SOMEDAY.

13:25.513 --> 13:27.139
- CHUM CHUM,
THIS THING IS AMAZING.

13:27.223 --> 13:29.934
BUT I WONDER.

13:32.811 --> 13:33.729
- [sniffing]

13:33.812 --> 13:35.105
EW, GROSS!

13:35.189 --> 13:38.067
[coughing]

13:38.150 --> 13:43.072
[gasping]

13:43.155 --> 13:44.240
- WE'LL TAKE IT, THANK YOU.

13:44.323 --> 13:45.199
CHUM CHUM.

13:48.160 --> 13:52.081
I TRUST WAD O' CASH IS AN
ACCEPTABLE FORM OF PAYMENT.

13:52.164 --> 13:53.123
- COLD CASH.

13:53.207 --> 13:54.416
CHICKA!

13:54.500 --> 13:55.417
[laughs]

13:55.501 --> 13:56.752
- YAY!

13:56.835 --> 13:59.004
- WHOO-HOO, WE'RE GONNA LIVE
IN A BUBBLE!

13:59.088 --> 14:00.005
[laughter]

14:00.089 --> 14:00.422
- SUCKERS.

14:00.506 --> 14:03.592
[laughing]

14:03.676 --> 14:06.679
[both cheering]

14:12.893 --> 14:16.855
[laughter]

14:16.939 --> 14:18.649
- [gasps]

14:18.732 --> 14:20.276
- CHUM CHUM,
HELP ME FLIP IT OVER.

14:20.359 --> 14:23.362
[laughter]

14:29.910 --> 14:30.452
[giggling]

14:30.536 --> 14:34.039
both: ONE, TWO, THREE!

14:34.123 --> 14:35.082
WHOO-HOO!

14:35.165 --> 14:37.585
[laughter]

14:37.668 --> 14:39.295
- UGH.

14:41.046 --> 14:43.215
[laughter]

14:47.428 --> 14:51.015
[laughter]

14:51.098 --> 14:54.393
[engines zooming]

14:59.857 --> 15:00.316
[engines firing]

15:00.399 --> 15:01.317
[screaming]

15:01.400 --> 15:05.112
[laughter]

15:07.072 --> 15:10.200
[crashing]

15:10.284 --> 15:11.327
- FROSTY FREEZY FREEZE?

15:11.410 --> 15:14.079
- DON'T MIND IF I DO.

15:14.163 --> 15:15.456
[crashing]

15:15.539 --> 15:16.665
- [snoring]

15:16.749 --> 15:17.333
- WHO WANTS A BURRITO?

15:17.416 --> 15:18.292
I'M BUYING.

15:18.375 --> 15:20.336
[laughter]

15:20.419 --> 15:20.794
I'M KIDDING.

15:20.878 --> 15:22.338
I'M JUST TAKING.

15:22.421 --> 15:23.464
[doorbell dings]

15:23.547 --> 15:26.508
- [grunting]

15:29.303 --> 15:31.722
[inhale sharply]

15:32.473 --> 15:36.810
[breathing deeply]

15:37.936 --> 15:38.979
- SORRY ABOUT THAT.

15:39.063 --> 15:40.189
- HEY!
- WHOOPSIE!

15:40.272 --> 15:41.190
- BE CAREFUL WITH THAT!

15:41.273 --> 15:41.649
- TERRIBLY SORRY.

15:41.732 --> 15:43.192
- WATCH OUT.

15:43.275 --> 15:44.234
- THAT WAS MY BUTT.

15:44.318 --> 15:45.361
- OOPS, CLEANUP, AISLE FOUR.

15:45.444 --> 15:46.528
- SOMEBODY'S GOT
TO CLEAN THAT UP,

15:46.612 --> 15:47.613
AND IT'S ME.

15:47.696 --> 15:48.781
-<i> NO PROBLEMO.</i>

15:50.282 --> 15:51.950
THAT'S "NO PROBLEM" IN SPANISH,
LENNY.

15:53.410 --> 15:54.536
- BE CAREFUL!

15:54.620 --> 15:57.081
- OH, WE GOT IT.

15:57.164 --> 15:59.291
- OH, NEVER MIND.

16:01.293 --> 16:04.546
- AH, SWEET FROSTY
FREEZY FREEZE.

16:04.630 --> 16:07.383
THIS IS GONNA TASTE SO GOOD
RIGHT ABOUT NOW.

16:07.466 --> 16:11.136
[both grunting]

16:11.220 --> 16:13.222
OKAY, LET'S TRY THAT AGAIN.

16:13.305 --> 16:14.807
AND...

16:14.890 --> 16:15.224
AH.

16:15.307 --> 16:17.226
AH?

16:17.309 --> 16:20.396
[grunting]

16:22.272 --> 16:23.691
I KNOW.

16:23.774 --> 16:25.776
WE'LL JUST PULL THEM IN THROUGH
THESE RUBBER ARM DEALIES.

16:25.859 --> 16:28.696
THEN THEY'LL BE INSIDE
THE BUBBLE.

16:28.779 --> 16:30.155
YOU'VE GOT TO PULL HARDER.

16:30.239 --> 16:32.199
[both groaning]

16:41.083 --> 16:42.960
- MY GREENBACKS!

16:46.213 --> 16:47.172
[explosion]

16:47.256 --> 16:50.008
NO!

16:50.092 --> 16:50.843
- TIME TO GO.

16:50.926 --> 16:54.763
- I AM GONNA BOP YOU INSIDE OUT.

16:54.847 --> 16:56.932
[grunts and groans]

16:57.015 --> 16:58.976
THAT FEELS ODDLY FAMILIAR.

16:59.059 --> 17:00.269
GRR!

17:00.352 --> 17:02.646
[grunting]

17:02.730 --> 17:03.564
- OH, THIS IS FUN!

17:03.647 --> 17:04.606
WE'RE LIKE POPCORN!

17:04.690 --> 17:07.067
- YEAH, POPCORN!

17:07.151 --> 17:09.111
- [grunting]

17:09.194 --> 17:10.194
[laughter]

17:10.279 --> 17:12.448
- OH, YOU ASKED FOR IT NOW.

17:12.531 --> 17:15.409
I AM GONNA UNLEASH
MY ULTIMATE WEAPON,

17:15.492 --> 17:16.492
THE H-BOP.

17:16.577 --> 17:17.661
[both gasp]

17:17.744 --> 17:22.750
PREPARE FOR DEATH BY BOP!

17:22.833 --> 17:25.794
[screaming]

17:27.003 --> 17:28.005
[explosion]

17:28.088 --> 17:29.381
- [screaming]

17:29.465 --> 17:30.966
- [screaming]

17:31.049 --> 17:31.925
- [laughing]

17:32.009 --> 17:32.217
OH, NO!

17:35.679 --> 17:38.849
CHIMP CHOMP!

17:38.932 --> 17:41.560
[electronic noises fading]

17:41.643 --> 17:43.479
- EW.

17:43.562 --> 17:45.063
HEY, WEREN'T WE ABOUT
TO TREAT OURSELVES

17:45.147 --> 17:47.566
TO A FROSTY FREEZY FREEZE?

17:47.649 --> 17:50.486
- I DO BELIEVE WE WERE.

17:50.569 --> 17:51.737
[electronic monkey noises]

17:51.820 --> 17:55.491
- CHIMP CHOMP, SPEAK TO ME!

17:55.574 --> 17:56.450
IT'S ME, BOOG.

17:56.533 --> 17:59.161
WHAT, THIS?

17:59.244 --> 18:00.704
IT ISN'T SO BAD.

18:00.788 --> 18:03.624
WE'LL GET DOC TO PATCH YOU UP
GOOD AS NEW IN NO TIME.

18:03.707 --> 18:05.125
I SWEAR.

18:05.209 --> 18:06.752
[electronic monkey noises]

18:06.835 --> 18:08.545
[dying electronic noises]

18:08.629 --> 18:10.964
CHIMP CHOMP?

18:11.048 --> 18:12.341
CHIMP CHOMP!

18:12.424 --> 18:13.842
COME BACK TO ME, CHIMP CHOMP!

18:13.926 --> 18:15.886
[whimpering]

18:15.969 --> 18:19.348
YOU KILL-SCREENED
MY CHIMP CHOMP!

18:19.431 --> 18:19.681
- [slurping]

18:19.765 --> 18:21.350
AH.

18:21.433 --> 18:22.851
- GET OUT OF THAT BUBBLE

18:22.935 --> 18:25.187
AND TAKE YOUR BOPPING
LIKE A MAN...

18:25.270 --> 18:25.687
S.

18:25.771 --> 18:27.731
[both giggling]

18:27.815 --> 18:30.484
- EH, TEMPTING OFFER,
BUT WE RESPECTFULLY DECLINE.

18:30.567 --> 18:32.861
- YEAH, IN HERE
WE'RE UNBOPPABLE.

18:32.945 --> 18:36.782
- WELL, YOU GOT TO COME OUT
OF THAT BUBBLE SOMETIME.

18:36.865 --> 18:38.158
- MM, I DON'T SEE WHY.

18:38.242 --> 18:45.207
- BECAUSE I DIDN'T SELL YOU
THE SPECIAL ATTACHMENT.

18:45.290 --> 18:46.583
[laughing]

18:46.667 --> 18:49.336
both: [gulping]

18:49.419 --> 18:51.964
UH-OH.

18:52.047 --> 18:54.508
- DON'T YOU JUST LOVE
THAT SOUND

18:54.591 --> 18:56.385
OF WETNESS?

18:56.468 --> 18:58.095
HEY, GET COMFORTABLE, BOYS.

18:58.178 --> 18:59.638
[slurping]

18:59.721 --> 19:02.891
IT'S GONNA BE A LONG NIGHT.

19:02.975 --> 19:03.851
[laughs]

19:03.934 --> 19:06.436
[both whimpering]

19:10.649 --> 19:11.650
- [snoring]

19:11.733 --> 19:13.777
HMM?

19:13.861 --> 19:15.153
HUH?

19:15.237 --> 19:17.489
SHH.

19:17.573 --> 19:18.574
- HUH?

19:18.657 --> 19:19.616
- BOOG'S GONE.

19:19.700 --> 19:20.742
NOW'S OUR CHANCE.

19:24.830 --> 19:27.082
[toilet flushes]

19:27.165 --> 19:28.750
[Chum Chum sighs]

19:28.834 --> 19:31.336
- OH, NOW I CAN THINK.

19:31.420 --> 19:32.963
LET'S GET SOMETHING TO EAT.

19:33.046 --> 19:34.298
I AM FAMISHED.

19:34.381 --> 19:34.840
- UH-HUH.

19:34.923 --> 19:39.720
- [deep breathing]

19:39.803 --> 19:41.138
- OH, I GUESS YOU'RE RIGHT.

19:41.221 --> 19:43.473
I'VE NEVER MET A MAN
NAMED NACHO.

19:45.893 --> 19:47.811
YOU KNOW, I'VE NEVER BEEN
IN THE FROSTY MART

19:47.895 --> 19:49.229
WHEN IT'S CLOSED.

19:49.313 --> 19:50.939
- OH, THAT'S PROBABLY 'CAUSE
IT NEVER CLOSES.

19:51.023 --> 19:51.607
IT'S OPEN 24 HOURS.

19:51.690 --> 19:53.609
- OH, RIGHT.

19:53.692 --> 19:55.485
SO HOW COME IT'S CLOSED NOW?

19:55.569 --> 19:56.528
- BEATS ME.

19:56.612 --> 19:58.488
[can rattling]

19:58.572 --> 20:00.574
- [deep breathing]

20:00.657 --> 20:01.199
BOP, BOP.

20:01.283 --> 20:03.785
- CHUM CHUM, IT'S A TRAP!

20:03.869 --> 20:08.457
- YOU ARE SO GONNA GET BOPPED.

20:08.540 --> 20:09.958
- BACK TO THE BUBBLE!

20:10.042 --> 20:10.584
[screaming]

20:10.667 --> 20:11.585
[crashing]

20:11.668 --> 20:15.380
- [laughing]

20:16.673 --> 20:18.842
WHOA, BEANS!

20:18.926 --> 20:19.468
- [screaming]

20:19.551 --> 20:20.510
[laughter]

20:20.594 --> 20:22.721
HA!

20:22.804 --> 20:24.431
- PTOO!

20:24.514 --> 20:27.476
- WELL, WELL, WELL.

20:27.559 --> 20:29.311
- READY TO GIVE UP
AND ADMIT DEFEAT LIKE A MAN?

20:29.394 --> 20:30.562
- UH!

20:30.646 --> 20:31.897
FINE.

20:31.980 --> 20:32.814
I GIVE UP.

20:32.898 --> 20:34.566
I KNOW WHEN I-I--

20:34.650 --> 20:36.860
[gasps]

20:36.944 --> 20:38.070
- BOOG?

20:38.153 --> 20:39.112
YOU OKAY?

20:39.196 --> 20:40.364
- [gasping]

20:40.447 --> 20:41.949
IT CAN'T BE.

20:42.032 --> 20:46.161
I'M HAVING A ALLERGY ATTACK!

20:46.244 --> 20:48.163
[gasping wildly]

20:48.246 --> 20:54.127
I GOT TO GET IN THE BUBBLE
BEFORE MY FACE EXPLODES!

20:54.211 --> 20:56.338
- QUICK, CHUM CHUM,
LET THE MAN IN.

20:59.925 --> 21:00.759
- THERE, THERE, BOOG.

21:00.842 --> 21:01.843
ARE YOU OKAY?

21:01.927 --> 21:05.764
- [laughing wildly]

21:07.057 --> 21:09.184
[roaring laughter]

21:09.267 --> 21:09.893
OH, I'M FINE.

21:09.977 --> 21:11.853
BUT YOU'RE NOT GONNA BE.

21:11.937 --> 21:14.189
- YOU WERE FAKING?

21:14.272 --> 21:16.817
BUT HOW DID YOU DO THAT
WITH YOUR FACE

21:16.900 --> 21:18.193
WITH THE LIPS AND THE FLIPS
AND THE TRIPS AND THE WHATNOTS?

21:18.276 --> 21:21.196
- OH, I GOT ALL KINDS
OF MAD SKILLS.

21:21.279 --> 21:22.364
YEAH!

21:22.447 --> 21:24.408
- SO WHO'S READY TO GET BOPPED,
HUH?

21:24.491 --> 21:26.284
AND IF YOU'RE HOPING
IT'LL BE OVER QUICK,

21:26.368 --> 21:26.994
YOU'RE WRONG!

21:27.077 --> 21:28.954
- OKAY, COME ON, BOOG.

21:29.037 --> 21:30.706
WE'RE ALL FRIENDS HERE.

21:30.789 --> 21:32.040
JUST TRY AND RELAX.

21:32.124 --> 21:37.129
- YEAH, YOU DON'T WANT BRING ON
ANOTHER FAKE ALLERGY ATTACK.

21:37.212 --> 21:39.423
[nervous laughter]

21:39.506 --> 21:40.048
[doorbell dings]

21:40.132 --> 21:41.258
- WELL, IF I WAS YOU,

21:41.341 --> 21:45.012
I'D BE MORE WORRIED
ABOUT YOUR OWN HEALTH,

21:45.095 --> 21:46.763
'CAUSE YOU'RE ABOUT TO HAVE IT
BOPPED OUT OF YOU.

21:46.847 --> 21:48.724
- [screaming]

21:48.807 --> 21:49.975
[helium hissing]

21:50.058 --> 21:52.728
END OF THE LINE, BOYS.

21:52.811 --> 21:54.855
[high-pitched voice]
YOU GOT THESE BOPS COMING!

21:54.938 --> 21:57.399
[laughter]

21:57.482 --> 21:58.734
- WHY YOU LAUGHING?

21:58.817 --> 22:00.027
[high-pitched voice]
- YOUR VOICE, IT'S FUNNY.

22:00.110 --> 22:02.112
[high-pitched voice]
- [laughs]

22:02.195 --> 22:03.071
SO IS OURS!

22:03.155 --> 22:04.072
- HEY, YOU'RE RIGHT.

22:04.156 --> 22:07.159
[laughter]

22:11.163 --> 22:12.581
[helium hissing]

22:12.664 --> 22:16.293
- OH, I'M GONNA BOP YOU SO HARD
WHEN I GET OUT OF HERE!

22:16.376 --> 22:18.795
MAN, IT'S HARD TO SOUND TOUGH
WITH THIS VOICE.

22:18.879 --> 22:21.173
- YEAH!

22:21.256 --> 22:22.799
I WONDER HOW HE'S GONNA
GET DOWN FROM THERE.

22:22.883 --> 22:23.425
- I DON'T KNOW.
pop!

22:23.508 --> 22:26.678
- STUPID POINTY MOON!

22:26.762 --> 22:28.555
[crashing]

22:28.638 --> 22:30.098
I'M STUCK IN A TREE!

22:30.182 --> 22:31.933
- YOU KNOW, I'D BE SCARED,

22:32.017 --> 22:35.896
BUT I'M TOO BUSY LAUGHING
AT THAT VOICE!

22:35.979 --> 22:36.855
[laughter]

22:36.938 --> 22:38.023
- ME TOO!

22:38.106 --> 22:39.441
[laughter]

22:39.524 --> 22:40.358
- NO, WAIT!

22:40.442 --> 22:42.319
I'M ALLERGIC TO CHIPMUNKS!

22:42.402 --> 22:43.695
[screaming]

